<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_270_r2l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt von lewff vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l4">meͣr <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l5"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır ſeıd der <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / dıe wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l6">der Stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> nehſt nach <expan>ſchıkte<ex>n</ex></expan> / niht <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l7"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc künıg <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> haben . Doch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l8">ſo ſeyn vnſer <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dıe Bıſchof von Paſſaw vnd von Maylan ~ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l10">Patrıarch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_270_r2l9">von fryawl </ab></add> vnd ~ der 
<add><l><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan></l></add> von vveinſperg noch bey vns . Dıe ſeinr <expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l11"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒukunft noch alls <expan>warte<ex>n</ex></expan> als wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> / So ſeyn vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l12">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> ~ den von Eger bey ʒweyen tagen brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l13"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> / dıe vns etwıeuıl meͣr <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / der etlıche kleglıch </ab>
