<ab facs="#facs_270_r2l15"><expan>ſchrıfte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> vnd ʒettel dıe wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅtſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
